              power-on
                 ↓
ROM on-chip → minimum boot loader
                 ↓
              enumerate as USB device → VID:PID
                 ↓
host → USB bulk transfer → packets:
                              ↓
                           check header: 12 bytes + CRC: 4 bytes
                              ↓
                           check payload: 508 bytes* + CRC: 4 bytes
                              ↓
                           write payload → RAM on chip
                 ↓
              execute firmware

----
*may be smaller for the last packet or zero for no payload
